(1)
259 Essex Street, east side, between Atlantic and Liberty Aves. The view shows the Church of St. Rita and Roctory. "a Roman Catholic
institution."
July 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from a different angle.
July 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr.
(3)
The same, showing the belfry.
July 27, 1939.
P. L. Sperr.
